room_title: Escape room "The Factory - A Gas Works Company" by Epic Escape Game in Muncie
room_description:
The Muncie natural gas factory is overheating and the town has been evacuated. You and your team of engineers must find your way into the factory and figure out how to shut it down before itâ€™s too late.
There are 2 identical rooms accommodating 8 people each. Parties smaller than 8 will be grouped together with others (as needed) as the game is more enjoyable working as a team. Groups booking more than 8 people will be split up into two rooms.
